  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When a creature within 15ft of you makes a melee attack, as a reaction, force the target to make a Wisdom (Perception) check vs your Dexterity (Sleight of Hand). <br />If you beat their check, you throw dirt in their eyes blinding them until the end of their next turn. <br />Alternatively, they can spend a bonus action wiping the dirt from their eyes, immediately ending the blinded condition.</p>",
